beer.beer_description:
Coffee/Vanilla/Oats

If you’re anything like us, that first cuppa coffee each morning is a requirement to function like a “normal” human being.

With that in mind we’ve teamed up with James @seventhwave_coffee again who’s Tsunami Blend adds hints of dark chocolate and tobacco leaf to this silky smooth breaky stout. Plus, with a base of Guatemalan Robusta its sure to give you the pick-me-up you need.

We also put every type of oat we could get our hands on into this beer. Flaked oats, malted oats, golden naked oats & roasted oats.

Nothing says breakfast like coffee, oats and a hint of vanilla!
